snippet.textDisplay:
1980's early 90's !!!
damn what an era and those were the ONLY days.. everything had some quality and balance..feel lucky to have been a part of it.

Zohaib Hassan being out of touch from signing since a while sung this very well and his heart out...can feel it in his voice,

Amir Zaki: You killed the guitars with such ease and patience.
Strings: Good Job. Request to mention C.S: Pakistan as the group name, as it may give some good waves around for the country. Not being nationalistic.
